snippet.title: Capcom Fighting All-Stars (Match Footage Collection)
snippet.description:
The Capcom 3D fighter that never saw release did have some footage pop up on the internet.  Most people have seen the trailer if they have any interest in the game at all but you may have missed some of this match footage.  

I don't know about my viewers but I would have loved to at least try out this game.

Check out this interview for more details:
https://game.capcom.com/cfn/sfv/column/132053
